data.description: Price Improvement!!! Fantastic 5BR Two Story brick home in Ashtynn Manor. Foyer opens to formal dining room or Office, huge great room w/gas log fireplace, Gourmet kitchen w/custom cabinets, granite, pantry, tile, breakfast bar and breakfast area. Crown molding, tall smooth ceilings thru-out main level. Main level offers Master Suite w/garden tub & separate shower, walk-in closet. Upper Level offers 4 bedrooms with walk-in closets, huge Bonus/media area. Near RSA gate 3. Only 5 mins to GRISSOM H.S.! Beautiful hardwood floors in main living area Supersized backyard is perfect for entertaining! Screened & open patio, w/privacy fence. Detached shed does not convey.
